<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Compte cree - BizHub</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        :root {
            --primary:      #ffbe33;
            --primary-dark: #e0a820;
            --dark:         #222831;
            --dark2:        #1a1f27;
            --white:        #ffffff;
            --light-bg:     #f8f8f8;
            --text-muted:   #666666;
            --border:       #ebebeb;
            --success-bg:   #ecfdf3;
            --success-text: #0c6b3d;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Lora', serif;
            background: var(--dark2);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(255,190,51,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 70% 80%, rgba(255,190,51,0.05) 0%, transparent 40%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .auth-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 480px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .auth-brand {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .auth-brand a {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .auth-brand a span { color: var(--primary); }
        .auth-container {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            padding: 48px 40px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .success-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: var(--success-bg);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        }
        .success-icon i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--success-text);
        }
        .auth-title {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Lora', serif;
        }
        .auth-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .email-box {
            background: var(--light-bg);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--dark);
        }
        .next-steps {
            text-align: left;
            background: #f0f7ff;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-left: 4px solid #1166ff;
        }
        .next-steps h4 {
            font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: #1166ff;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .next-steps ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .next-steps li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
        .resend-box {
            border: 1px dashed var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .resend-box p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .resend-box form {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        .resend-box input[type="email"] {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .resend-box button {
            border: 0;
            background: var(--dark);
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .auth-footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .auth-footer a {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .flash-box {
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .flash-success { background: var(--success-bg); color: var(--success-text); border: 1px solid rgba(12,107,61,0.2); }
        .flash-error { background: #fff1f2; color: #9f1239; border: 1px solid rgba(159,18,57,0.2); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="auth-wrapper">
        <div class="auth-brand">
            <a href="{{ path('app_index') }}">Biz<span>Hub</span></a>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-container">
            {% for message in app.flashes('success') %}
                <div class="flash-box flash-success">{{ message }}</div>
            {% endfor %}

            {% for message in app.flashes('error') %}
                <div class="flash-box flash-error">{{ message }}</div>
            {% endfor %}

            <div class="success-icon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-circle-check"></i>
            </div>

            <h1 class="auth-title">Verifiez votre email</h1>
            <p class="auth-subtitle">
                Un lien de verification a ete envoye a votre adresse email. 
                Cliquez sur ce lien pour activer votre compte.
            </p>

            <div class="email-box">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> {{ email }}
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>Prochaines etapes</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Ouvrez votre boite email</li>
                    <li>Cherchez le message de BizHub</li>
                    <li>Cliquez sur le lien de verification</li>
                    <li>Completez la configuration MFA</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="resend-box">
                <p>Vous n'avez pas recu l'email ?</p>
                <form method="post" action="{{ path('app_verify_email_resend') }}">
                    <input type="hidden" name="_token" value="{{ csrf_token('resend_verification_email') }}" />
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Votre email" value="{{ email }}" required />
                    <button type="submit">Renvoyer</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="auth-footer">
                Deja verifie ? <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}">Se connecter</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>